    "body": "<img width=\"1318\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2020-11-11 at 06 34 20\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/98747037-482a0e80-23e9-11eb-9631-fde393c2c998.png\">\r\n\r\nalso we have to improve `deleteNonCanonicalBlocks` with the below for loop, that's why I lost all of my last peers after all\r\n```\r\nconst nonCanonicalSummaries = this.forkChoice\r\n      .forwardIterateBlockSummaries()\r\n      .filter(\r\n        (summary) =>\r\n          summary.slot < finalizedSlot && !this.forkChoice.isDescendant(summary.blockRoot, this.finalized.root)\r\n      );\r\n```\r\n\r\nit takes more than 30 minutes for this function\r\n```\r\n2020-11-11 04:40:16 [CHORES]           ^[[32minfo^[[39m: @@@ Archive Blocks: processed chunk lowerBound=77568, upperBound=77614, size=77614\r\n185454 2020-11-11 05:14:35 [SYNC]          ^[[36mverbose^[[39m: Status with future finalized epoch 22129: 0x0b0cb543c397629921bc8fe2ac0d40cd29eb2fc4b3372a4ffeee131917def568\r\n```",
